## 📘 Overview

The **Toyota Cloud Alignment Model (TCAM)** is a strategic coordination system designed to:  
- Align Toyota's global technical and ethical systems  
- Leverage Korea’s underutilized IT workforce  
- Operate cloud-based development pipelines  
- And realize gospel-centered, public-purpose governance in East Asia

> **"Structure over location. People over numbers. Order over chaos."**

